short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhancing User Experience with Advanced Safety, Customization, and Efficient Automation Features.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A security enhancement has been implemented by adding an additional layer of protection to irreversible actions such as 'Delete all chats' and 'Delete Account.' This added layer of security has also been extended to the logout process.
